4&#x27; stitchTiles=&#x27;stitch&#x27;/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width=&#x27;100%25&#x27; height=&#x27;100%25&#x27; filter=&#x27;url(%23noise)&#x27;/%3E%3C/svg%3E&quot;)\"></div></div></div><div class=\"break-inside-avoid relative group\"><div class=\"w-full aspect-[4/5] bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-300 via-sky-200 to-blue-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden relative\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-30\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/20 to-transparent\"></div></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-10\" style=\"background-image:url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox=&#x27;0 0 256 256&#x27; xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%3E%3Cfilter id=&#x27;noise&#x27;%3E%3CfeTurbulence type=&#x27;fractalNoise&#x27; baseFrequency=&#x27;0.9&#x27; numOctaves=&#x27;4&#x27; stitchTiles=&#x27;stitch&#x27;/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width=&#x27;100%25&#x27; height=&#x27;100%25&#x27; filter=&#x27;url(%23noise)&#x27;/%3E%3C/svg%3E&quot;)\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-2 right-2 w-6 h-6 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-md\"><svg class=\"w-3 h-3 text-white\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z\"></path></svg></div></div></div></div><div class=\"px-5 py-4 border-t border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/80 flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-400 to-orange-400\"></div><div class=\"w-24 h-3 bg-slate-300 rounded-full\"></div></div><button class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-primary text-white text-xs font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-primary font-body\">Confirmar seleção</button></div></div><div class=\"absolute -top-4 -right-4 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-card border border-slate-100 px-4 py-3 flex items-center gap-2.5 animate-float\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-green-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-foreground font-body leading-tight\">Seleção recebida!</p><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 font-body\">Ana confirmou 4 fotos</p></div></div><div class=\"absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-card border border-slate-100 px-4 py-3 flex items-center gap-2.5\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary-50 flex items-center justify-center\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-primary\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-foreground font-body leading-tight\">Acesso por PIN</p><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 font-body\">Seguro e simples</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"como-funciona\" class=\"py-20 lg:py-28 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16 lg:mb-20\"><span class=\"inline-block font-body text-sm font-semibold text-primary bg-primary-50 border border-primary-100 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4\">Como funciona</span><h2 class=\"font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4 leading-tight\">Do upload à seleção final,<!-- --> <span class=\"text-primary\">tudo em 4 passos</span></h2><p class=\"font-body text-lg text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Simples para você, intuitivo para seu cliente. Sem complicação, sem fricção.</p></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"hidden lg:block absolute top-14 left-[calc(12.5%+32px)] right-[calc(12.5%+32px)] h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-200 via-sky-200 via-teal-200 to-emerald-200\"></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 lg:gap-6\"><div class=\"relative flex flex-col items-center text-center group\"><div class=\"relative mb-6\"><div class=\"w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-primary-50 flex items-center justify-center relative z-10 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-card\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-user-plus w-7 h-7 text-primary\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle><line x1=\"19\" x2=\"19\" y1=\"8\" y2=\"14\"></line><line x1=\"22\" x2=\"16\" y1=\"11\" y2=\"11\"></line></svg></div><div class=\"absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm z-20\"><span class=\"font-body text-xs font-bold text-slate-400\">1</span></div></div><h3 class=\"font-heading text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3\">Crie sua conta</h3><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed max-w-[220px]\">Em minutos, sem cartão de crédito. Comece o seu teste grátis de 14 dias imediatamente.</p><div class=\"lg:hidden mt-6 text-slate-300\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6 mx-auto\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"relative flex flex-col items-center text-center group\"><div class=\"relative mb-6\"><div class=\"w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-sky-50 flex items-center justify-center relative z-10 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-card\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-upload w-7 h-7 text-sky-600\"><path d=\"M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4\"></path><polyline points=\"17 8 12 3 7 8\"></polyline><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"15\"></line></svg></div><div class=\"absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm z-20\"><span class=\"font-body text-xs font-bold text-slate-400\">2</span></div></div><h3 class=\"font-heading text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3\">Faça o upload</h3><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed max-w-[220px]\">Envie as fotos do trabalho diretamente pela plataforma. Organize em álbuns por cliente ou evento.</p><div class=\"lg:hidden mt-6 text-slate-300\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6 mx-auto\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"relative flex flex-col items-center text-center group\"><div class=\"relative mb-6\"><div class=\"w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-teal-50 flex items-center justify-center relative z-10 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-card\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-share2 w-7 h-7 text-teal-600\"><circle cx=\"18\" cy=\"5\" r=\"3\"></circle><circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\"></circle><circle cx=\"18\" cy=\"19\" r=\"3\"></circle><line x1=\"8.59\" x2=\"15.42\" y1=\"13.51\" y2=\"17.49\"></line><line x1=\"15.41\" x2=\"8.59\" y1=\"6.51\" y2=\"10.49\"></line></svg></div><div class=\"absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm z-20\"><span class=\"font-body text-xs font-bold text-slate-400\">3</span></div></div><h3 class=\"font-heading text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3\">Compartilhe o link</h3><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed max-w-[220px]\">Seu cliente acessa com um PIN seguro, no celular. Sem precisar criar conta ou baixar aplicativo.</p><div class=\"lg:hidden mt-6 text-slate-300\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6 mx-auto\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"relative flex flex-col items-center text-center group\"><div class=\"relative mb-6\"><div class=\"w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-50 flex items-center justify-center relative z-10 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-card\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-square-check-big w-7 h-7 text-emerald-600\"><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path><path d=\"M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm z-20\"><span class=\"font-body text-xs font-bold text-slate-400\">4</span></div></div><h3 class=\"font-heading text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3\">Receba a seleção</h3><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed max-w-[220px]\">As fotos favoritas chegam no seu painel organizadas. Sem e-mails confusos ou listas no WhatsApp.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-16 text-center\"><a href=\"/cadastro\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-primary text-white font-body font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-primary-600 transition-all duration-200 shadow-primary hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5 text-base\">Começar agora — é grátis</a></div></div></section><section id=\"funcionalidades\" class=\"py-20 lg:py-28 bg-background\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><span class=\"inline-block font-body text-sm font-semibold text-secondary bg-amber-50 border border-amber-100 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4\">Funcionalidades</span><h2 class=\"font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4 leading-tight\">Tudo que você precisa,<!-- --> <span class=\"text-primary\">nada que atrapalha</span></h2><p class=\"font-body text-lg text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Desenvolvido especificamente para o fluxo de trabalho de fotógrafos profissionais brasileiros.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8\"><div class=\"group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 border border-violet-100 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-violet-50 rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity\"></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-violet-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-folder-open w-5 h-5 text-violet-600\"><path d=\"m6 14 1.5-2.9A2 2 0 0 1 9.24 10H20a2 2 0 0 1 1.94 2.5l-1.54 6a2 2 0 0 1-1.95 1.5H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3.9a2 2 0 0 1 1.69.9l.81 1.2a2 2 0 0 0 1.67.9H18a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v2\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-heading text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3\">Álbuns organizados</h3><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">Separe cada trabalho em seu próprio álbum. Casamento, ensaio, evento — tudo no lugar certo, sempre.</p></div></div><div class=\"group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 border border-primary-100 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-primary-50 rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity\"></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-primary-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lock w-5 h-5 text-primary\"><rect width=\"18\" height=\"11\" x=\"3\" y=\"11\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-heading text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3\">Acesso por PIN</h3><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">Sem login para o cliente — só o PIN que você define. Simples, seguro, sem fricção.</p></div></div><div class=\"group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 border border-rose-100 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-rose-50 rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity\"></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-rose-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart w-5 h-5 text-rose-600\"><path d=\"M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-heading text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3\">Seleção intuitiva</h3><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">O cliente clica nas fotos favoritas direto pelo celular. Uma experiência elegante que impressiona.</p></div></div><div class=\"group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 border border-teal-100 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-teal-50 rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity\"></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-teal-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-download w-5 h-5 text-teal-600\"><path d=\"M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4\"></path><polyline points=\"7 10 12 15 17 10\"></polyline><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"15\" y2=\"3\"></line></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-heading text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3\">Receba a seleção pronta</h3><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">Veja quais fotos foram selecionadas no seu painel, organizadas e prontas para editar.</p></div></div><div class=\"group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 border border-sky-100 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-sky-50 rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity\"></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-sky-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-cloud w-5 h-5 text-sky-600\"><path d=\"M17.5 19H9a7 7 0 1 1 6.71-9h1.79a4.5 4.5 0 1 1 0 9Z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-heading text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3\">Seus trabalhos na nuvem</h3><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">Tudo salvo e acessível de qualquer lugar. No estúdio, em casa ou na rua.</p></div></div><div class=\"group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 border border-amber-100 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-amber-50 rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity\"></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-amber-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sliders-vertical w-5 h-5 text-amber-600\"><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"4\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"4\" y1=\"10\" y2=\"3\"></line><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"8\" y2=\"3\"></line><line x1=\"20\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"16\"></line><line x1=\"20\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"3\"></line><line x1=\"2\" x2=\"6\" y1=\"14\" y2=\"14\"></line><line x1=\"10\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"8\" y2=\"8\"></line><line x1=\"18\" x2=\"22\" y1=\"16\" y2=\"16\"></line></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-heading text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3\">Limite de seleção</h3><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">Você define quantas fotos o cliente pode escolher. Sem surpresas, sem desentendimentos.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"precos\" class=\"py-20 lg:py-28 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><span class=\"inline-block font-body text-sm font-semibold text-primary bg-primary-50 border border-primary-100 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4\">Planos e preços</span><h2 class=\"font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4 leading-tight\">Invista no seu<!-- --> <span class=\"text-primary\">crescimento profissional</span></h2><p class=\"font-body text-lg text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Comece de graça e faça upgrade quando precisar. Sem fidelidade, sem multa.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 lg:gap-5 items-start\"><div class=\"relative rounded-2xl flex flex-col transition-all duration-300 bg-white border border-slate-200 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"p-6 lg:p-7 flex flex-col flex-1\"><div class=\"mb-5\"><h3 class=\"font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-1 text-foreground\">Período Teste</h3><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-slate-500\">Explore tudo sem compromisso</p></div><div class=\"mb-6\"><div><span class=\"font-heading text-4xl font-bold text-foreground\">Grátis</span><p class=\"font-body text-sm mt-0.5 text-slate-400\">por 14 dias</p></div></div><div class=\"h-px mb-6 bg-slate-100\"></div><ul class=\"space-y-3 flex-1 mb-7\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><div class=\"w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 bg-primary-50\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" 