</div></div><div class=\"h-px mb-6 bg-slate-100\"></div><ul class=\"space-y-3 flex-1 mb-7\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><div class=\"w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 bg-primary-50\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check w-3 h-3 text-primary\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600\">100 GB de armazenamento</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><div class=\"w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 bg-primary-50\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check w-3 h-3 text-primary\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600\">Álbuns ilimitados</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><div class=\"w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 bg-primary-50\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check w-3 h-3 text-primary\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600\">Fotos ilimitadas por álbum</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><div class=\"w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 bg-primary-50\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check w-3 h-3 text-primary\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600\">Acesso por PIN</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><div class=\"w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 bg-primary-50\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check w-3 h-3 text-primary\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600\">Link compartilhável</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><div class=\"w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 bg-primary-50\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check w-3 h-3 text-primary\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600\">Limite de seleção por álbum</span></li></ul><button class=\"w-full py-3.5 rounded-xl font-body font-semibold text-sm transition-all duration-200 bg-primary text-white hover:bg-primary-600 shadow-primary hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5 active:translate-y-0\">Assinar Avançado</button></div></div></div><p class=\"text-center font-body text-sm text-slate-400 mt-8\">Comece com 14 dias grátis no período de teste. Cancele quando quiser, sem burocracia.</p></div></section><section class=\"py-20 lg:py-28 bg-background\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><span class=\"inline-block font-body text-sm font-semibold text-primary bg-primary-50 border border-primary-100 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4\">Depoimentos</span><h2 class=\"font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4 leading-tight\">O que dizem os<!-- --> <span class=\"text-primary\">fotógrafos Fotux</span></h2><p class=\"font-body text-lg text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Histórias reais de fotógrafos que transformaram seu fluxo de trabalho.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 border border-slate-100\"><div class=\"absolute top-6 right-6 opacity-10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-quote w-12 h-12 text-primary fill-current\"><path d=\"M16 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path><path d=\"M5 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"flex gap-1 mb-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-secondary fill-current\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-secondary fill-current\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-secondary fill-current\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-secondary fill-current\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-secondary fill-current\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg></div><blockquote class=\"font-body text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6 relative z-10\">“<!-- -->Antes eu perdia horas no WhatsApp confirmando quais fotos o cliente queria. Agora mando o link e em 24h tenho a seleção completa. Minha vida mudou.<!-- -->”</blockquote><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 pt-6 border-t border-slate-100\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-400 to-pink-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-body font-bold text-sm shadow-sm flex-shrink-0\">AF</div><div><p class=\"font-heading font-semibold text-foreground leading-tight\">Ana Carolina Ferreira</p><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-slate-400 mt-0.5\">Fotografa de casamentos<!-- --> · <!-- -->São Paulo</p></div></div></div><div class=\"relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 border border-slate-100\"><div class=\"absolute top-6 right-6 opacity-10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-quote w-12 h-12 text-primary fill-current\"><path d=\"M16 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path><path d=\"M5 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"flex gap-1 mb-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-secondary fill-current\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-secondary fill-current\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-secondary fill-current\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-secondary fill-current\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-secondary fill-current\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg></div><blockquote class=\"font-body text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6 relative z-10\">“<!-- -->Meus clientes adoram a facilidade. Mais de um me perguntou se era um app exclusivo meu. Parece muito profissional — e isso faz diferença no meu negócio.<!-- -->”</blockquote><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 pt-6 border-t border-slate-100\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-400 to-purple-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-body font-bold text-sm shadow-sm flex-shrink-0\">RM</div><div><p class=\"font-heading font-semibold text-foreground leading-tight\">Rafael Monteiro</p><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-slate-400 mt-0.5\">Fotógrafo de eventos<!-- --> · <!-- -->Rio de Janeiro</p></div></div></div><div class=\"relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 border border-slate-100\"><div class=\"absolute top-6 right-6 opacity-10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-quote w-12 h-12 text-primary fill-current\"><path d=\"M16 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path><path d=\"M5 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"flex gap-1 mb-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-secondary fill-current\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-secondary fill-current\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-secondary fill-current\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-secondary fill-current\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star w-4 h-4 text-secondary fill-current\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"></polygon></svg></div><blockquote class=\"font-body text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6 relative z-10\">“<!-- -->O trial me convenceu na primeira semana. Nunca mais vou voltar para o Google Drive. É simples, bonito e funciona exatamente como eu precisava.<!-- -->”</blockquote><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 pt-6 border-t border-slate-100\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400 to-orange-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-body font-bold text-sm shadow-sm flex-shrink-0\">JS</div><div><p class=\"font-heading font-semibold text-foreground leading-tight\">Juliana Santos</p><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-slate-400 mt-0.5\">Fotógrafa de ensaios<!-- --> · <!-- -->Belo Horizonte</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-16 grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 lg:gap-8\"><div class=\"text-center\"><p class=\"font-heading text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-1\">1.200+</p><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-slate-500\">Fotógrafos ativos</p></div><div class=\"text-center\"><p class=\"font-heading text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-1\">48mil+</p><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-slate-500\">Álbuns criados</p></div><div class=\"text-center\"><p class=\"font-heading text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-1\">98%</p><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-slate-500\">Taxa de satisfação</p></div><div class=\"text-center\"><p class=\"font-heading text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-1\">24h</p><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-slate-500\">Tempo médio de seleção</p></div></div></div></section><section id=\"faq\" class=\"py-20 lg:py-28 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><span class=\"inline-block font-body text-sm font-semibold text-primary bg-primary-50 border border-primary-100 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4\">Dúvidas frequentes</span><h2 class=\"font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4 leading-tight\">Perguntas frequentes</h2><p class=\"font-body text-lg text-slate-500\">Tudo que você precisa saber antes de começar.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"border rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 border-primary-200 bg-primary-50/30 shadow-elegant\"><button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 p-6 text-left\"><span class=\"font-body font-semibold leading-snug text-primary\">Meu cliente precisa criar uma conta?</span><div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 transition-colors bg-primary text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-minus w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path></svg></div></button><div class=\"transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out max-h-40 opacity-100 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"px-6 pb-6\"><p class=\"font-body text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">Não. O cliente acessa a galeria pelo link único que você compartilha, com um PIN seguro que você mesmo define. Sem cadastro, sem senha, sem aplicativo para baixar. Só um link e um PIN.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 border-slate-200 bg-white hover:border-slate-300\"><button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 p-6 text-left\"><span class=\"font-body font-semibold leading-snug text-foreground\">Quantas fotos posso enviar?</span><div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 transition-colors bg-slate-100 text-slate-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-plus w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"M12 5v14\"></path></svg></div></button><div class=\"transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out max-h-0 opacity-0 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"px-6 pb-6\"><p class=\"font-body text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">Depende do plano escolhido. No Trial gratuito, você pode enviar até 300 fotos por mês. No plano Básico, 1.000 fotos. No Pro, até 5.000 fotos. E no Avançado, até 15.000 fotos mensais.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 border-slate-200 bg-white hover:border-slate-300\"><button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 p-6 text-left\"><span class=\"font-body font-semibold leading-snug text-foreground\">Como funciona o período de teste?</span><div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 transition-colors bg-slate-100 text-slate-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-plus w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"M12 5v14\"></path></svg></div></button><div class=\"transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out max-h-0 opacity-0 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"px-6 pb-6\"><p class=\"font-body text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">Você tem 14 dias completamente grátis para testar todas as funcionalidades, sem precisar cadastrar cartão de crédito. Se não gostar, simplesmente não assina. Sem cobranças, sem pegadinhas.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 border-slate-200 bg-white hover:border-slate-300\"><button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 p-6 text-left\"><span class=\"font-body font-semibold leading-snug text-foreground\">As fotos ficam seguras na plataforma?</span><div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 transition-colors bg-slate-100 text-slate-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-plus w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"M12 5v14\"></path></svg></div></button><div class=\"transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out max-h-0 opacity-0 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"px-6 pb-6\"><p class=\"font-body text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">Sim. Seus arquivos são armazenados com criptografia e protegidos por sistemas de segurança robustos. Além disso, o acesso às galerias é sempre protegido pelo PIN que você configura.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 border-slate-200 bg-white hover:border-slate-300\"><button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 p-6 text-left\"><span class=\"font-body font-semibold leading-snug text-foreground\">Posso cancelar quando quiser?</span><div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 transition-colors bg-slate-100 text-slate-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-plus w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"M12 5v14\"></path></svg></div></button><div class=\"transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out max-h-0 opacity-0 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"px-6 pb-6\"><p class=\"font-body text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">Sim, sem nenhuma burocracia. Você pode cancelar sua assinatura a qualquer momento, sem fidelidade ou multa. O acesso permanece ativo até o fim do período já pago.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-200 border-slate-200 bg-white hover:border-slate-300\"><button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4 p-6 text-left\"><span class=\"font-body font-semibold leading-snug text-foreground\">Funciona no celular do cliente?</span><div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 transition-colors bg-slate-100 text-slate-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-plus w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"M12 5v14\"></path></svg></div></button><div class=\"transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out max-h-0 opacity-0 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"px-6 pb-6\"><p class=\"font-body text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">Sim. A galeria foi desenvolvida com foco em dispositivos móveis e funciona perfeitamente em qualquer smartphone, seja Android ou iPhone, sem precisar instalar nada.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-10 text-center p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200\"><p class=\"font-body text-slate-600 mb-3\">Ainda tem alguma dúvida?</p><a href=\"https://wa.me/5511999999999?text=Ol%C3%A1%2C%20tenho%20uma%20d%C3%BAvida%20sobre%20o%20Fotux\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-body font-semibold text-sm text-white bg-[#25D366] px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl hover:bg-[#20BD5C] transition-colors shadow-sm\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 fill-current\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-